  "detailHtml": "<section id='value-details' class='mt-12 rounded-3xl border border-white/5 bg-slate-900/50 p-6 sm:p-10'>\n  <h2 class='text-2xl font-bold text-white'>Wie Popur X5 die Box wirklich sauber hält</h2>\n  <p class='mt-3 text-sm text-white/70'>Diese Details spiegeln die offizielle Popur-X5-Seite wider: genau wie das Split-Litter-System funktioniert, warum Katzen es schnell akzeptieren und die leisen, praktischen Features, die das Leben damit erleichtern.</p>\n\n  <div class='mt-8 grid gap-6 md:grid-cols-2'>\n    <article class='flex flex-col rounded-2xl border border-white/10 bg-slate-950/60 p-5'>\n      <figure class='overflow-hidden rounded-xl border border-white/10 bg-slate-950/80'>\n        <img\n          class='lazyload h-40 w-full object-cover'\n          src='https://popur.com/cdn/shop/files/Gives-you-a-30-day-break-between-changing-bags.webp?v=1746712748&width=416'\n          data-src='https://popur.com/cdn/shop/files/Gives-you-a-30-day-break-between-changing-bags.webp?v=1746712748&width=2000'\n          alt='Popur X5 verschafft dir bis zu 30 Tage Pause zwischen Beutelwechseln'\n        />\n        <noscript>\n          <img\n            class='h-40 w-full object-cover'\n            src='https://popur.com/cdn/shop/files/Gives-you-a-30-day-break-between-changing-bags.webp?v=1746712748&width=2000'\n            alt='Popur X5 verschafft dir bis zu 30 Tage Pause zwischen Beutelwechseln'\n          />\n        </noscript>\n      </figure>\n      <div class='mt-4 space-y-2 text-sm text-white/80'>\n        <h3 class='text-lg font-semibold text-white'>Bis zu 30 Tage zwischen Beutelwechseln</h3>\n        <p>Der Popur-X5-Mülleimer fasst bis zu einen Monat Abfall eines einzelnen Katers – perfekt für Mehrkatzenhaushalte, volle Zeitpläne und Reisende.</p>\n      </div>\n    </article>\n\n    <article class='flex flex-col rounded-2xl border border-white/10 bg-slate-950/60 p-5'>\n      <figure class='overflow-hidden rounded-xl border border-white/10 bg-slate-950/80'>\n        <img\n          class='lazyload h-40 w-full object-cover'\n          src='https://popur.com/cdn/shop/files/Traps-99.9-percent-odor-sensible-to-you-and-your-cats.webp?v=1746713158&width=416'\n          data-src='https://popur.com/cdn/shop/files/Traps-99.9-percent-odor-sensible-to-you-and-your-cats.webp?v=1746713158&width=2000'\n          alt='Popur X5 hält über 99 % des Geruchs in einem versiegelten Behälter zurück'\n        />\n        <noscript>\n          <img\n            class='h-40 w-full object-cover'\n            src='https://popur.com/cdn/shop/files/Traps-99.9-percent-odor-sensible-to-you-and-your-cats.webp?v=1746713158&width=2000'\n            alt='Popur X5 hält über 99 % des Geruchs in einem versiegelten Behälter zurück'\n          />\n        </noscript>\n      </figure>\n      <div class='mt-4 space-y-2 text-sm text-white/80'>\n        <h3 class='text-lg font-semibold text-white'>Eigener Mülleimer, der Geruch versiegelt</h3>\n        <p>Statt Klumpen in der Schale zu lassen, lagert X5 jeden Abfall in einem hinteren Mülleimer und schließt Gase und Dämpfe im Beutel ein, damit nichts in den Wohnraum entweicht.</p>\n      </div>\n    </article>\n\n    <article class='flex flex-col rounded-2xl border border-white/10 bg-slate-950/60 p-5'>\n      <figure class='overflow-hidden rounded-xl border border-white/10 bg-slate-950/80'>\n        <img\n          class='lazyload h-40 w-full object-cover'\n          src='https://popur.com/cdn/shop/files/Scrapes-off-sticky-clumps-proactively-to-ensure-zero-mess.webp?v=1746713162&width=416'\n          data-src='https://popur.com/cdn/shop/files/Scrapes-off-sticky-clumps-proactively-to-ensure-zero-mess.webp?v=1746713162&width=2000'\n          alt='Popur X5 löst klebrige Klumpen proaktiv, damit nichts haften bleibt'\n        />\n        <noscript>\n          <img\n            class='h-40 w-full object-cover'\n            src='https://popur.com/cdn/shop/files/Scrapes-off-sticky-clumps-proactively-to-ensure-zero-mess.webp?v=1746713162&width=2000'\n            alt='Popur X5 löst klebrige Klumpen proaktiv, damit nichts haften bleibt'\n          />\n        </noscript>\n      </figure>\n      <div class='mt-4 space-y-2 text-sm text-white/80'>\n        <h3 class='text-lg font-semibold text-white'>Löst klebrige Klumpen, bevor sie antrocknen</h3>\n        <p>Wenn Klumpen am Liner oder an den Seitenwänden kleben, reibt X5 seinen Filter dagegen, um sie zu lösen – die Schale bleibt sauber statt schlammig.</p>\n      </div>\n    </article>\n\n    <article class='flex flex-col rounded-2xl border border-white/10 bg-slate-950/60 p-5'>\n      <figure class='overflow-hidden rounded-xl border border-white/10 bg-slate-950/80'>\n        <img\n          class='lazyload h-40 w-full object-cover'\n          src='https://popur.com/cdn/shop/files/Wipe-handily-and-restore-as-new-in-60-seconds.webp?v=1746713160&width=416'\n          data-src='https://popur.com/cdn/shop/files/Wipe-handily-and-restore-as-new-in-60-seconds.webp?v=1746713160&width=2000'\n          alt='Popur X5 wird in 60 Sekunden wie neu sauber gewischt'\n        />\n        <noscript>\n          <img\n            class='h-40 w-full object-cover'\n            src='https://popur.com/cdn/shop/files/Wipe-handily-and-restore-as-new-in-60-seconds.webp?v=1746713160&width=2000'\n            alt='Popur X5 wird in 60 Sekunden wie neu sauber gewischt'\n          />\n        </noscript>\n      </figure>\n      <div class='mt-4 space-y-2 text-sm text-white/80'>\n        <h3 class='text-lg font-semibold text-white'>In ~60 Sekunden wie neu</h3>\n        <p>Flache, glatte Flächen und ein offenes Layout lassen sich schnell abwischen – Grundreinigung fühlt sich wie ein kurzer Reset an, nicht wie eine Komplettdemontage.</p>\n      </div>\n    </article>\n  </div>\n\n  <div class='mt-12 rounded-2xl border border-white/10 bg-slate-950/60 p-5'>\n    <h3 class='text-xl font-semibold text-white'>Gebaut, wie echte Katzen die Box nutzen</h3>\n    <p class='mt-3 text-sm text-white/70'>Die offizielle Popur-Galerie zeigt, dass X5 für alle Katzentypen gedacht ist: die meisten, die offene Boxen mögen, große Rassen mit Platzbedarf, Kätzchen, die Sicherheit brauchen, und Senioren, die einen niedrigen Einstieg brauchen.</p>\n    <div class='mt-4 grid gap-4 sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3'>\n      <figure class='flex flex-col overflow-hidden rounded-2xl border border-white/10 bg-slate-950/80'>\n        <img\n          class='lazyload h-32 w-full object-cover'\n          src='https://popur.com/cdn/shop/files/Benefits-for-cats-most-kitties-enjoy-doing-business-in-a-ventilated-and-open-top-potty-x5-desktop.webp?v=1746770560&width=416'\n          data-src='https://popur.com/cdn/shop/files/Benefits-for-cats-most-kitties-enjoy-doing-business-in-a-ventilated-and-open-top-potty-x5-desktop.webp?v=1746770560&width=2200'\n          alt='Die meisten Katzen mögen eine offene, belüftete Box wie Popur X5'\n        />\n        <noscript>\n          <img\n            class='h-32 w-full object-cover'\n            src='https://popur.com/cdn/shop/files/Benefits-for-cats-most-kitties-enjoy-doing-business-in-a-ventilated-and-open-top-potty-x5-desktop.webp?v=1746770560&width=2200'\n            alt='Die meisten Katzen mögen eine offene, belüftete Box wie Popur X5'\n          />\n        </noscript>\n        <figcaption class='flex-1 px-4 pb-4 pt-3 text-xs text-white/70'>Die meisten Katzen bevorzugen eine offene, belüftete Toilette, die natürlich wirkt, statt einen dunklen, engen Trommelraum.</figcaption>\n      </figure>\n\n      <figure class='flex flex-col overflow-hidden rounded-2xl border border-white/10 bg-slate-950/80'>\n        <img\n          class='lazyload h-32 w-full object-cover'\n          src='https://popur.com/cdn/shop/files/Benefits-for-cats-giant-breeds-like-Main-Coons-will-also-feel-comfy-in-the-24-inch-interior-x5-desktop.webp?v=1746773914&width=416'\n          data-src='https://popur.com/cdn/shop/files/Benefits-for-cats-giant-breeds-like-Main-Coons-will-also-feel-comfy-in-the-24-inch-interior-x5-desktop.webp?v=1746773914&width=2200'\n          alt='Große Rassen fühlen sich im 24-Zoll-Innenraum des Popur X5 wohl'\n        />\n        <noscript>\n          <img\n            class='h-32 w-full object-cover'\n            src='https://popur.com/cdn/shop/files/Benefits-for-cats-giant-breeds-like-Main-Coons-will-also-feel-comfy-in-the-24-inch-interior-x5-desktop.webp?v=1746773914&width=2200'\n            alt='Große Rassen fühlen sich im 24-Zoll-Innenraum des Popur X5 wohl'\n          />\n        </noscript>\n        <figcaption class='flex-1 px-4 pb-4 pt-3 text-xs text-white/70'>Große Rassen wie Maine Coons haben im 24-Zoll-Innenraum noch Platz zum Drehen und Scharren.</figcaption>\n      </figure>\n\n      <figure class='flex flex-col overflow-hidden rounded-2xl border border-white/10 bg-slate-950/80'>\n        <img\n          class='lazyload h-32 w-full object-cover'\n          src='https://popur.com/cdn/shop/files/Benefits-for-cats-even-kittens-may-use-this-perfectly-safe-pinch-free-ActiveShield-mechanism-x5-desktop.webp?v=1746773938&width=416'\n          data-src='https://popur.com/cdn/shop/files/Benefits-for-cats-even-kittens-may-use-this-perfectly-safe-pinch-free-ActiveShield-mechanism-x5-desktop.webp?v=1746773938&width=2200'\n          alt='Popur X5 nutzt einen klemmfreien ActiveShield-Mechanismus, sicher auch für Kätzchen'\n        />\n        <noscript>\n          <img\n            class='h-32 w-full object-cover'\n            src='https://popur.com/cdn/shop/files/Benefits-for-cats-even-kittens-may-use-this-perfectly-safe-pinch-free-ActiveShield-mechanism-x5-desktop.webp?v=1746773938&width=2200'\n            alt='Popur X5 nutzt einen klemmfreien ActiveShield-Mechanismus, sicher auch für Kätzchen'\n          />\n        </noscript>\n        <figcaption class='flex-1 px-4 pb-4 pt-3 text-xs text-white/70'>Der klemmfreie ActiveShield-Mechanismus schützt neugierige Kätzchen während des Reinigungszyklus.</figcaption>\n      </figure>\n\n      <figure class='flex flex-col overflow-hidden rounded-2xl border border-white/10 bg-slate-950/80'>\n        <img\n          class='lazyload h-32 w-full object-cover'\n          src='https://popur.com/cdn/shop/files/Benefits-for-cats-senior-cats-and-short-legs-are-well-accommodated-by-the-rather-low-entryway-x5-desktop.webp?v=1746779465&width=416'\n          data-src='https://popur.com/cdn/shop/files/Benefits-for-cats-senior-cats-and-short-legs-are-well-accommodated-by-the-rather-low-entryway-x5-desktop.webp?v=1746779465&width=2200'\n          alt='Senioren und kurzbeinige Katzen profitieren vom niedrigen Einstieg des Popur X5'\n        />\n        <noscript>\n          <img\n            class='h-32 w-full object-cover'\n            src='https://popur.com/cdn/shop/files/Benefits-for-cats-senior-cats-and-short-legs-are-well-accommodated-by-the-rather-low-entryway-x5-desktop.webp?v=1746779465&width=2200'\n            alt='Senioren und kurzbeinige Katzen profitieren vom niedrigen Einstieg des Popur X5'\n          />\n        </noscript>\n        <figcaption class='flex-1 px-4 pb-4 pt-3 text-xs text-white/70'>Ein niedriger Einstieg erleichtert Senioren, Kurzbeinern und Katzen mit weniger Mobilität den Zugang.</figcaption>\n      </figure>\n\n      <figure class='flex flex-col overflow-hidden rounded-2xl border border-white/10 bg-slate-950/80'>\n        <img\n          class='lazyload h-32 w-full object-cover'\n          src='https://popur.com/cdn/shop/files/Benefits-for-cats-corner-vertical-pee-ers-kickers-diggers-and-the-skittish-ones-feel-indulged-by-the-higher-guard-x5-desktop.webp?v=1746770626&width=416'\n          data-src='https://popur.com/cdn/shop/files/Benefits-for-cats-corner-vertical-pee-ers-kickers-diggers-and-the-skittish-ones-feel-indulged-by-the-higher-guard-x5-desktop.webp?v=1746770626&width=2200'\n          alt='Katzen, die in die Ecke pinkeln oder stark scharren, profitieren vom höheren Heckschutz des Popur X5'\n        />\n        <noscript>\n          <img\n            class='h-32 w-full object-cover'\n            src='https://popur.com/cdn/shop/files/Benefits-for-cats-corner-vertical-pee-ers-kickers-diggers-and-the-skittish-ones-feel-indulged-by-the-higher-guard-x5-desktop.webp?v=1746770626&width=2200'\n            alt='Katzen, die in die Ecke pinkeln oder stark scharren, profitieren vom höheren Heckschutz des Popur X5'\n          />\n        </noscript>\n        <figcaption class='flex-1 px-4 pb-4 pt-3 text-xs text-white/70'>Ein höherer Heckschutz verwöhnt Eck-Pinkler, Sand-Kicker und scheue Katzen, die etwas mehr Abschirmung wollen.</figcaption>\n      </figure>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n\n  <div class='mt-12 rounded-2xl border border-dashed border-brand-500/40 bg-slate-950/60 p-5'>\n    <h3 class='text-xl font-semibold text-white'>Weitere Alltags-Details, die den Unterschied machen</h3>\n    <p class='mt-3 text-sm text-white/70'>Der Bereich What's more auf Popur.com hebt kleine, aber wichtige Bequemlichkeiten hervor, die X5 im Alltag leichter machen.</p>\n    <div class='mt-4 grid gap-4 sm:grid-cols-3'>\n      <figure class='flex flex-col overflow-hidden rounded-2xl border border-white/10 bg-slate-950/80'>\n        <img\n          class='lazyload h-28 w-full object-cover'\n          src='https://popur.com/cdn/shop/files/More-features-use-any-clumping-litter-x5.webp?v=1746770961&width=416'\n          data-src='https://popur.com/cdn/shop/files/More-features-use-any-clumping-litter-x5.webp?v=1746770961&width=1250'\n          alt='Popur X5 funktioniert mit jeder üblichen Klumpstreu'\n        />\n        <noscript>\n          <img\n            class='h-28 w-full object-cover'\n            src='https://popur.com/cdn/shop/files/More-features-use-any-clumping-litter-x5.webp?v=1746770961&width=1250'\n            alt='Popur X5 funktioniert mit jeder üblichen Klumpstreu'\n          />\n        </noscript>\n        <figcaption class='flex-1 px-4 pb-4 pt-3 text-xs text-white/70'>Nutze jede Klumpstreu, die du schon kennst, statt teure proprietäre Nachfüllungen.</figcaption>\n      </figure>\n\n      <figure class='flex flex-col overflow-hidden rounded-2xl border border-white/10 bg-slate-950/80'>\n        <img\n          class='lazyload h-28 w-full object-cover'\n          src='https://popur.com/cdn/shop/files/More-features-no-contact-inside-out-bag-x5.webp?v=1746770965&width=416'\n          data-src='https://popur.com/cdn/shop/files/More-features-no-contact-inside-out-bag-x5.webp?v=1746770965&width=1250'\n          alt='Popur X5 nutzt einen umgekrempelten Beutel, damit du Abfall nicht berührst'\n        />\n        <noscript>\n          <img\n            class='h-28 w-full object-cover'\n            src='https://popur.com/cdn/shop/files/More-features-no-contact-inside-out-bag-x5.webp?v=1746770965&width=1250'\n            alt='Popur X5 nutzt einen umgekrempelten Beutel, damit du Abfall nicht berührst'\n          />\n        </noscript>\n        <figcaption class='flex-1 px-4 pb-4 pt-3 text-xs text-white/70'>Das Inside-Out-Beutel-Design hält deine Hände fern, wenn es Zeit ist, den Müll rauszubringen.</figcaption>\n      </figure>\n\n      <figure class='flex flex-col overflow-hidden rounded-2xl border border-white/10 bg-slate-950/80'>\n        <img\n          class='lazyload h-28 w-full object-cover'\n          src='https://popur.com/cdn/shop/files/More-features-library-quiet-lower-than-40dBA-x5.webp?v=1746770971&width=416'\n          data-src='https://popur.com/cdn/shop/files/More-features-library-quiet-lower-than-40dBA-x5.webp?v=1746770971&width=1250'\n          alt='Popur X5 läuft leise unter 40 dBA, bibliotheksleise'\n        />\n        <noscript>\n          <img\n            class='h-28 w-full object-cover'\n            src='https://popur.com/cdn/shop/files/More-features-library-quiet-lower-than-40dBA-x5.webp?v=1746770971&width=1250'\n            alt='Popur X5 läuft leise unter 40 dBA, bibliotheksleise'\n          />\n        </noscript>\n        <figcaption class='flex-1 px-4 pb-4 pt-3 text-xs text-white/70'>Reinigungszyklen unter 40 dBA sind bibliotheksleise – wecken nicht und erschrecken keine sensiblen Katzen.</figcaption>\n      </figure>\n\n      <figure class='flex flex-col overflow-hidden rounded-2xl border border-white/10 bg-slate-950/80'>\n        <img\n          class='lazyload h-28 w-full object-cover'\n          src='https://popur.com/cdn/shop/files/More-features-pair-it-with-the-App-x5.webp?v=1746770974&width=416'\n          data-src='https://popur.com/cdn/shop/files/More-features-pair-it-with-the-App-x5.webp?v=1746770974&width=1250'\n          alt='Popur X5 kann mit einer App gekoppelt werden für mehr Kontrolle'\n        />\n        <noscript>\n          <img\n            class='h-28 w-full object-cover'\n            src='https://popur.com/cdn/shop/files/More-features-pair-it-with-the-App-x5.webp?v=1746770974&width=1250'\n            alt='Popur X5 kann mit einer App gekoppelt werden für mehr Kontrolle'\n          />\n        </noscript>\n        <figcaption class='flex-1 px-4 pb-4 pt-3 text-xs text-white/70'>Kopple optional mit der App, um Nutzung zu verfolgen und Einstellungen anzupassen, ohne vor der Box zu stehen.</figcaption>\n      </figure>\n\n      <figure class='flex flex-col overflow-hidden rounded-2xl border border-white/10 bg-slate-950/80'>\n        <img\n          class='lazyload h-28 w-full object-cover'\n          src='https://popur.com/cdn/shop/files/More-features-move-around-easily-with-casters-x5.webp?v=1746770979&width=416'\n          data-src='https://popur.com/cdn/shop/files/More-features-move-around-easily-with-casters-x5.webp?v=1746770979&width=1250'\n          alt='Popur X5 hat Rollen, damit du ihn leicht bewegen kannst'\n        />\n        <noscript>\n          <img\n            class='h-28 w-full object-cover'\n            src='https://popur.com/cdn/shop/files/More-features-move-around-easily-with-casters-x5.webp?v=1746770979&width=1250'\n            alt='Popur X5 hat Rollen, damit du ihn leicht bewegen kannst'\n          />\n        </noscript>\n        <figcaption class='flex-1 px-4 pb-4 pt-3 text-xs text-white/70'>Integrierte Rollen erleichtern das Verschieben von X5 beim Putzen oder Umstellen.</figcaption>\n      </figure>\n\n      <figure class='flex flex-col overflow-hidden rounded-2xl border border-white/10 bg-slate-950/80'>\n        <img\n          class='lazyload h-28 w-full object-cover'\n          src='https://popur.com/cdn/shop/files/More-features-place-on-carpet-or-any-surfaces-x5.webp?v=1746770982&width=416'\n          data-src='https://popur.com/cdn/shop/files/More-features-place-on-carpet-or-any-surfaces-x5.webp?v=1746770982&width=1250'\n          alt='Popur X5 kann auf Teppich oder anderen Flächen stehen'\n        />\n        <noscript>\n          <img\n            class='h-28 w-full object-cover'\n            src='https://popur.com/cdn/shop/files/More-features-place-on-carpet-or-any-surfaces-x5.webp?v=1746770982&width=1250'\n            alt='Popur X5 kann auf Teppich oder anderen Flächen stehen'\n          />\n        </noscript>\n        <figcaption class='flex-1 px-4 pb-4 pt-3 text-xs text-white/70'>Stelle X5 auf Teppich oder andere gängige Böden ohne Spezialmatte.</figcaption>\n      </figure>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n</section>",
